        <mxCell id="8zs2SkQTrW1NaClQp68N-18" value="&lt;div&gt;T=actiongs.length&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;智能体执行actions[t]这个动作&lt;/div&gt;计算后验概率&lt;div&gt;P(G1|&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: -apple-system, Roboto, SegoeUI, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Meiryo UI&amp;quot;, Meiryo, &amp;quot;Arial Unicode MS&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;ξ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;)与&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;P(G2|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: -apple-system, Roboto, SegoeUI, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Meiryo UI&amp;quot;, Meiryo, &amp;quot;Arial Unicode MS&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;ξ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;)并分别将其归一化&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;处理&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
